creator: Radiodar
descriptionHtml:
If you are not in Japan and want to listen to Japanese radio, this app is your first choice.

There are over 200 popular radio channels collected in the app.

If you know the URL of new streaming radio stations, you can add your own favourite stations. Mark your favourite channels to put them on top of the list for quick access.

Radio will be playing in background so that you can perform other activities.

Shutdown timer allows you to turn off the radio automatically.
